</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_425" id="211v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Wilhelm Frawnhofer,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, herczog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                        Bayern etc. <expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her hofmeister, als <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> lieber
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgeselle Sigmund Stromeyr von
                        der Rosen nehst <add>bey euch gewesen ist</add> von sölcher habe und
                        kauffmanschaft wegen, als <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan></add> zollner czu Landshute den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> aufgehalten und bekümert hat, also
                        hat uns derselb <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan> ratgesell wol czu wissen
                        getan, wie im <add>ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan></add> darynne gar
                        fürderlich gewegen und geraten gewesen sey mit besunder guten
                                <expan>anweisu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>, des wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz dancken; und als derselb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> ratgeselle
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> darümb <add>czu </add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<add><expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> gnedigen</add>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> herczog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<add>und <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan></add> kümt,
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir euch
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ratgesellen fürbaz mer <add>darynne</add> mit
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> günstigen
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und <expan>anweisu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<add>wöllet gütlich</add>
<expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan>
<expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab><add><expan>Ritt<ex>er</ex></expan></add>
